<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
     <style>
       .product{
        display: flex;
        /* flex-direction: column-reverse; */
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: brown;
        height: 300px;
        padding: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 30px;
       }

        .box{
            border: 1px solid black;
            height: 100px;
            width: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-style: italic;
            background-color: beige;
        }
     </style>
    
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Flex Gives display in 1 Dimensional - either Row or column
    Flex byDefault Display in Row Format -->

    <div class="product">
        <div class="box">Cake.</div>
        <div class="box">Cookies.</div>
        <div class="box">Pastry.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: monospace;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        h1{
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .team{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card{
            border-radius: 12px;
            background-color: bisque;
            width: 220px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px black;
        }

        button{
            padding: 20px;
            border: none;
            background-color: blue;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        h3{
            color: red;
            font-size: 25px;
        }

        p{
            color: #666;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        img{
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid red;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Meet Our Awesome Team</h1>

    <div class="team">
      
        <div class="card">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">

        </div>

         <div class="card">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,">

        </div>

         <div class="card">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,">

        </div>

         <div class="card">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            <h3>Romana</h3>
            <p>UI/UX Developer</p>
            <button>Linkdln</button>
        </div>

        

    </div>
</body>
</html>
